improved_metadata.title: Sunshine Shirts: The Screen Printing Anthem
improved_metadata.description: This song celebrates the hustle and energy of a screen printing shop, where Mike and Nick work hard to create vibrant shirts day and night. It's a catchy tune about the rhythm of the process and the joy of creation.
improved_metadata.key_lyrics: Printing T's day and night, sunshine shirts burning bright
